<plot>Anna works as a waitress in a small café. Although she is quite good looking she suffers from an inferior complex - she considers herself as unattractive since she has to wear thick glasses. Without wearing them she can hardly realize what is happening in front of her. One day she falls in love with a customer, a young man who suddenly shows up in the café every single day. But Anna does not dare to speak to him, of course, having her glasses on her nose. Logically there can be only one solution - Anna decides to take the glasses off and practices to move blindly in the café in a night session. The next day arrives and Anna tries to find her way.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?016164</url></doc>
